OL,3,CPolitician calls for urgent action
OL,4,Cover island's dilapidated runway
OL,6,FAn Alderney politician is calling for
OL,7,Furgent action after flooding
OL,8,Ftemporarily closed the island's runway.
OL,10,FDamage caused by recent storms meant
OL,11,Fthe runway became unusable by the
OL,12,Fevening of Friday 31 January.
OL,14,FEngineers were called out and
OL,15,Fconducted critical maintenance works
OL,16,Fovernight; however, the runway could
OL,17,Fnot safely reopen and an emergency
OL,18,Fassessment was conducted on Saturday
OL,19,Fafternoon (1 February).
