OL,3,CPolitician calls for urgent action
OL,4,Cover island's dilapidated runway
OL,6,FSteve Roberts, one of Alderney's
OL,7,Fpoliticians, says this latest problem
OL,8,Fhighlights the need for the States of
OL,9,FGuernsey to approve immediate funding
OL,10,Ffor the runway's repairs to be
OL,11,Fundertaken.
OL,13,FGuernsey's Policy and Resources
OL,14,FCommittee scrapped their plans to
OL,15,Fextend the landing strip and build a
OL,16,Fnew terminal in Alderney after costs
OL,17,Frose from an estimated #12.2 million
OL,18,Fto #37 million last summer.
OL,20,FBut Alderney residents say action is
OL,21,Fneeded.
