OL,3,CPolitician calls for urgent action
OL,4,Cover island's dilapidated runway
OL,6,FAlderney Represenative Steve Roberts
OL,7,Fsays: "The runway refurbishment must
OL,8,Fbe brought forward as soon as
OL,9,Fpossible. It needs upgrading, not
OL,10,Fpatching, which is costing a fortune
OL,11,Fanyway.
OL,13,F"It really is a lifeline to two
OL,14,Fthousand Bailiwick taxpayers."
OL,16,FThis weekend's problems come after a
OL,17,Fvisit from the Civil Aviation
OL,18,FAuthority raised concerns that the
OL,19,Frunway might be forced to close
OL,20,Findefinitely if repairs are not
OL,21,Fprioritised.
